        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "And there he had almost slain me, and from us he took his horse and departed, and in an evil time we met with him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000018_000019",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000018_000019.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "By my faith, said Sir Tristram, I shall never rest till that I find him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000018_000020",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000018_000020.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "And then Sir Gawaine asked him his name.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000018_000021",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000018_000021.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "Then he said: My name is Sir Tristram.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000018_000022",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000018_000022.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "And so either told other their names, and then departed Sir Tristram and rode his way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "What tidings with you, said Sir Tristram, with you knights?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "Not good, said these knights.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "Why so? said Sir Tristram; I pray you tell me, for I ride to seek a knight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
