        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "CHAPTER four.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000021_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000021_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "And when he saw them lie on the earth he took his bridle, and rode forth on his way, and his man Gouvernail with him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000022_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000022_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "And this is the cause why I am so loath to have ado with you; for I must fight within these three days with a good knight, and as valiant as any is now living, and if I be hurt I shall not be able to do battle with him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000022_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000022_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "But, fair knight, said Sir Sagramore, tell us your name.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "And in that same place was the fair lady Colombe slain, that was love unto Sir Lanceor; for after he was dead she took his sword and thrust it through her body.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000024_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000024_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "And at that time Merlin prophesied that in that same place should fight two the best knights that ever were in Arthur's days, and the best lovers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000024_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000024_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "When he came nigh Sir Tristram he said on high: Ye be welcome, sir knight, and well and truly have ye holden your promise.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000024_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000024_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "So they stood and wept both, and made great dole when they saw the bright swords over covered with blood of their bodies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "Then at the last spake Sir Launcelot and said: Knight, thou fightest wonderly well as ever I saw knight, therefore, an it please you, tell me your name.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "Sir, said Sir Tristram, that is me loath to tell any man my name.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3148_4666_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3148/4666/3148_4666_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "Truly, said Sir Launcelot, an I were required I was never loath to tell my name.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
