        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3148",
        "content": "And then they both forthwithal went to the stone, and set them down upon it, and took off their helms to cool them, and either kissed other an hundred times.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
